message: 1、升级卡模块的刷入脚本到最新的版本，以解决在kernelSU中刷入生成的模块后出现的各种问题。||2、适配Material 3。||3、修复xposed/EdXposed/LSPosed特性设置开关失效的问题。||4、修复已知bug
message_en: 1. Upgrade the flashing script of the card module to the latest version to solve various problems that occur after flashing the generated module in kernelSU.||2. Adapt to Material 3.||3. Fix the problem that the xposed/EdXposed/LSPosed feature setting switch fails.||4. Fix known bugs.
